_Layer 1 (Physical Layer)_
на физическом уровне какой кабель мы используем 
what cable type of cable 
dumb devices they only repeat signal
01 01 01 01 01  # one zero 
lamp
Лампочка горит 1 
ламочка выключена 0
cable Rj45 connect your comp or switch

RJ-45 cable and ports
tia/eia 568 b
Crossover cables
T-568A and T-568B

Straight-thru cables
Typically use T-568B on both ends but could also use T-568A


Асинхронно делаешь запрос потом друзья услышают звуковое сообщения
синхронно должны общать одновременно

Time-division multiplexing 
exmaple tv 4 members everyone want to watch tv and everyone want to take to turn
use tv in some period of time 

Statistical-Time-Division Multiplexing (StatTDM)
i can use tv anytime what i want when tv free

Frequency Division Multiplexing (FDM)

examples at layer 1
cables:
1 ethernet 
2 fiber optic 

radio frequencies
1 wifi
2 bluetooth

Infrastructure devices
1 hubs
2 wireless Access Points 

dumb devices they only repeat signal 

